page_0:
"Daniir,

Is it wrong if I am looking forward to attending the funeral ceremony of Priest Mailu? I can already imagine the richly decorated people passing me by as the procession slowly moves southwards, following the Last Path. It's the first time I am allowed to see a funeral of a priest, and Healer Naza even agreed that I'll be assisting the Censer Call!

I'm a bit ashamed, though. I was too nervous to ask him how such a call works. All I know is that it can summon the spirit of a deceased person. Can you explain the procedure to me, please?

Ruitan"